measurements.description: Twelve flowers and 67 buds on three up to 30-cm branched inflorescences; dorsal sepal oblong, white faintly overlaid coerulea; lateral sepals ovate, white faintly overlaid coerulea; petals oblong, slightly porrect, white faintly overlaid coerulea; lip spatulate, white overlaid blue-lavender transitioning to yellow proximally, sidelobes narrow, upright, callus bright yellow spotted purple; column white overlaid coerulea, anther cap white; substance medium; texture crystalline.
